{
  "id": "69b22c21d6ea49d3289cf048",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:仕様変更あるある",
  "created": 1773284410,
  "updated": 1773284440,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b22c21d6ea49d3289cf048",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:仕様変更あるある",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284410,
      "updated": 1773284410
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3a0000000000bc6132",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284410,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6133",
      "text": "はいはーい！今日のテーマは「仕様変更あるある」ね〜。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6134",
      "text": "ゲーム開発とかアプリ作りとかで、あとから「やっぱこれ変えて」って言われるやつ。あれマジで地獄って聞くんだけどｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6135",
      "text": "りか、そのへんどうなん？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6136",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6137",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6138",
      "text": "結論から言うと、かなり頻発する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6139",
      "text": "ソフトウェア開発では「要件変更（requirements change）」と呼ばれる現象だね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc613a",
      "text": "例えば、最初に",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc613b",
      "text": " Aの機能を作る",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc613c",
      "text": "と決めたのに、途中で",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc613d",
      "text": " やっぱBにして",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc613e",
      "text": " いやCも追加で",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc613f",
      "text": "となる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6140",
      "text": "この結果、設計 → 実装 → テストの流れが崩壊する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6141",
      "text": "いわゆる「スコープクリープ」だ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6142",
      "text": "参考:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6143",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scope_creep",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6144",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6145",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6146",
      "text": "あーーーそれ聞いたことある！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6147",
      "text": "なんか[** 「ちょっとだけ機能足して」って言われるやつ]でしょ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6148",
      "text": "で、その「ちょっと」がラスボス級にデカくなるやつｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6149",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc614a",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc614b",
      "text": "（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc614c",
      "text": "まあ……それは、まるで物語を書いている最中に",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc614d",
      "text": "「やっぱり主人公を変えましょう」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc614e",
      "text": "「この世界は魔法ではなく科学にしましょう」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc614f",
      "text": "と告げられるようなものですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6150",
      "text": "書き手の方は、さぞや戸惑われることでしょう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6151",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6152",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6153",
      "text": "あーーそれヤバいｗｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6154",
      "text": "ジャンル変更パッチじゃんそれ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6155",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6156",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6157",
      "text": "実際、その比喩はかなり正確。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6158",
      "text": "ソフトウェアは依存関係でできている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6159",
      "text": "だから一箇所変えると、別の部分も壊れる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc615a",
      "text": "これを[** 変更の波及（ripple effect）]と言う。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc615b",
      "text": "例：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc615c",
      "text": " ログイン方法を変える",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc615d",
      "text": " → 認証処理が変わる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc615e",
      "text": " → セキュリティ仕様が変わる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc615f",
      "text": " → UIも変更",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6160",
      "text": "つまり「ちょっとの変更」が全体改修になる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6161",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6162",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6163",
      "text": "うわ出たｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6164",
      "text": "ドミノ倒しバグ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6165",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6166",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6167",
      "text": "（静かに笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6168",
      "text": "それは、湖に石を投げたときの波紋のようですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6169",
      "text": "小さな一石でも、円は遠くまで広がりますもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc616a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc616b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc616c",
      "text": "そのため、開発では普通",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc616d",
      "text": "[** 変更管理（change management）]を行う。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc616e",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc616f",
      "text": " 変更内容を記録",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6170",
      "text": " 影響範囲を分析",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6171",
      "text": " 優先度を決定",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6172",
      "text": "というプロセスを通す。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6173",
      "text": "ただし現実では、これが守られないことも多い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6174",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6175",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6176",
      "text": "あっ察しｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6177",
      "text": "「今日中に直して」って言われるやつだｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6178",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6179",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc617a",
      "text": "そう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc617b",
      "text": "緊急仕様変更という名のイベント。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc617c",
      "text": "開発者のHPが削られる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc617d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc617e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc617f",
      "text": "まあ……それは、嵐の中で航路を変える船のようですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6180",
      "text": "乗組員の方々は、きっと大忙しでしょう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6181",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6182",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6183",
      "text": "あやの例えが文学すぎるｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6184",
      "text": "でもさ、なんでそんなに仕様変わるの？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6185",
      "text": "最初に決めとけばよくない？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6186",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6187",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6188",
      "text": "いい質問。理由は主に3つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6189",
      "text": " 1. 最初は誰も正解がわからない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc618a",
      "text": "  ユーザーのニーズは後から見える。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc618b",
      "text": " 2. 市場が変わる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc618c",
      "text": "  競合やトレンドが動く。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc618d",
      "text": " 3. 人間は途中でアイデアを思いつく",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc618e",
      "text": "  つまり仕様変更は、ある程度は避けられない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc618f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6190",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6191",
      "text": "それはまるで、旅路の途中で",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6192",
      "text": "思いがけない景色に出会い、道を変えるようなものですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6193",
      "text": "当初の地図どおりには進めない……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6194",
      "text": "人生にも、よくあることですもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6195",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6196",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6197",
      "text": "あーなるほど。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6198",
      "text": "仕様変更＝人生の寄り道説ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc6199",
      "text": "でもさ、りか的に一番ヤバい仕様変更って何？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc619a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc619b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc619c",
      "text": "一番危険なのはこれ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc619d",
      "text": "「今のままで、でも全部作り直して」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc619e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc619f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61a0",
      "text": "意味不明すぎて草ｗｗｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61a1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61a2",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61a3",
      "text": "（肩をすくめて微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61a4",
      "text": "それは……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61a5",
      "text": "詩の言葉をそのままにして、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61a6",
      "text": "すべてを書き直せと言われるようなものですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61a7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61a8",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61a9",
      "text": "要点をまとめる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61aa",
      "text": "仕様変更あるある",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61ab",
      "text": " 「ちょっと変更」が巨大化",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61ac",
      "text": " 一箇所変えると全体に波及",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61ad",
      "text": " 緊急変更が突然降ってくる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61ae",
      "text": " 理由はだいたい「やっぱりこっちがいい」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61af",
      "text": "開発者はこれを",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61b0",
      "text": "[** 宿命（デスティニー）] として受け入れる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61b1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61b2",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61b3",
      "text": "出たｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61b4",
      "text": "エンジニアの運命ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61b5",
      "text": "でもまあ、ゲームのアップデートもそうだよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61b6",
      "text": "ユーザー「ここ直して！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61b7",
      "text": "開発「了解！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61b8",
      "text": "→ 別のバグ爆誕",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61b9",
      "text": "このループｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61ba",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61bb",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61bc",
      "text": "（やさしく笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61bd",
      "text": "それでも世界は、少しずつ良くなっていくのでしょうね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61be",
      "text": "試行錯誤という名の物語を重ねながら。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61bf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61c0",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61c1",
      "text": "その通り。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61c2",
      "text": "ソフトウェア開発とは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61c3",
      "text": "終わらない改善のプロセスだ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61c4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61c5",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61c6",
      "text": "ということで今日の結論！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61c7",
      "text": "仕様変更は避けられない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61c8",
      "text": "でもエンジニアのSAN値は削れる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61c9",
      "text": "おつかれさまでしたーｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c3b0000000000bc61ca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284411,
      "updated": 1773284411
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c490000000000bc61cb",
      "text": "#2026-03-12",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284426,
      "updated": 1773284440
    },
    {
      "id": "69b22c4b0000000000bc61cc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773284427,
      "updated": 1773284427
    }
  ]
}